---
/**
 * Legacy redirect — /history/ → /en/history/.
 *
 * The drafting-history tree migrated under [lang]/ in step 4.4. This static
 * page exists to preserve any inbound link to the unprefixed legacy URL.
 * Caddy will also 301 these at the proxy layer (per i18n decision note);
 * this stub is a fallback for build/preview environments that don't run
 * the proxy rules.
 */
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Redirecting…</title>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=/en/history/" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="/en/history/" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
</head>
<body>
  <p>This page has moved. <a href="/en/history/">Continue to the new location.</a></p>
</body>
</html>
